    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Matribus Auf<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>nis</abbr></expan> <lb n="2"/>Nepotinius <lb n="3"/>Nepotianus <lb n="4"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> pro se et <lb n="5"/>suis <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Albino et Maxi</ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>mo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ädikula mit Resten einer Darstellung der drei sitzenden Matronen.</p>
            </div>
